    <introduction>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p><em>Dr Kristen Knowles is an evolutionary psychologist at Queen Margaret University (QMU), where she applies her research on social perception to understanding political decision-making and leadership. She is a lecturer in biological psychology as well as the Programme Leader for the BSc (Hons) Psychology programme.</em></p>]]></Value>
